Package edu.mmatfb.cpre288.GUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatedBubbleChart
    JavaFX bubble chart to display scanner readings and the bump and cliff and edge sensors
    ChartController
    Thread-safe type used by the application to interact with the bubble chart
    ChartObstacle
    Internally holds the x, y, and radius of a scanned object to be sent to the AnimatedBubbleChart
    ChartTester
    used for testing the chart when the CyBot is not connected or a more specific input is required AnimatedBubbleChart must be modified to call this
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EdgeDirection
    Holds which CyBot sensor was triggered by a boundary, bump, or cliff even though there are only 2 bump sensors, they should use FRONT_LEFT and FRONT_RIGHT
    EdgeType
    Specifies the type of edge the cybot hits
